title: Ognjanci
text:
Ognjanci (, ) is a <a href="village">village</a> in the <a href="Municipalities%20of%20North%20Macedonia">municipality</a> of <a href="Petrovec%20Municipality">Petrovec</a>, <a href="North%20Macedonia">North Macedonia</a>.
